OL,3,CDFDS Seaways apologise after
OL,4,Cwheelchair user left in their van
OL,5,Cduring crossing
OL,7,FIt was alleged in the States that the
OL,8,Fferry's lift had been closed, but DFDS
OL,9,FSeaways have confirmed to ITV News
OL,10,Fthat it was a "serious mistake" in the
OL,11,Fboarding process.
OL,13,FDeputy Tadier asked the Minister:
OL,14,F"Does he accept that this situation
OL,15,Fwas both inhumane and degrading to the
OL,16,Findividual in question, and will he
OL,17,Fconduct his own investigation to
OL,18,Funderstand what took place to make
OL,19,Fsure it does not reoccur?"
