OL,4,Cwheelchair user left in their van
OL,5,Cduring crossing
OL,7,FDeput Morel responded: "This incident
OL,8,Fwas clearly unacceptable and falls a
OL,9,Flong way short of DFDS' standards."
OL,11,FThe Minister is now considering asking
OL,12,Fthe harbour master to investigate
OL,13,Fwhether the company broke the law.
OL,15,FDFDS has apologised, saying: "We fully
OL,16,Frecognise that the passenger's
OL,17,Fexperience was unacceptable and regret
OL,18,Fprofoundly that it occurred."
