OL,7,FClarifying the circumstances of the
OL,8,Fincident, DFDS stated that the lift on
OL,9,Fboard was "fully operational", with
OL,10,Fthe mistake being made in boarding.
OL,12,FThey stated: "The passenger ` who had
OL,13,Fcorrectly notified DFDS of his
OL,14,Faccessibility needs in advance ` was
OL,15,Fmistakenly left waiting on the quay
OL,16,Fwhile other vehicles began boarding.
