OL,3,CDFDS Seaways apologise after
OL,4,Cwheelchair user left in their van
OL,5,Cduring crossing
OL,7,F"By the time the disabled passenger's
OL,8,Fvehicle was directed on board, the
OL,9,Floading pattern meant the passenger
OL,10,Fcould not safely reach the lift in his
OL,11,Fwheelchair.
OL,13,F"The passenger was informed of the
OL,14,Fsituation before boarding and offered
OL,15,Fthe option of transferring to a later
OL,16,Fsailing on another vessel.
