OL,3,CDFDS Seaways apologise after
OL,4,Cwheelchair user left in their van
OL,5,Cduring crossing
OL,7,F"This was a serious mistake on our
OL,8,Fpart, and we are deeply sorry to the
OL,9,Fpassenger for the distress and
OL,10,Finconvenience caused."
OL,12,FThe ferry service added that they were
OL,13,Freviewing their procedures to
OL,14,Fprioritise disabled passengers during
OL,15,Fboarding, and will meet with Jersey
OL,16,Fgovernment's disability and inclusion
OL,17,Fteam to review further improvements.
